      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, parts car, or budget runabout? This one isn\u2019t pretty, but it\u2019s an honest car with plenty of potential for the right buyer. A great option for someone handy, a first project, or anyone who wants a low-cost way into ownership without spending a fortune. Priced fairly for what it is, and offered by someone who believes in being straightforward and easy to deal with.",
