    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, straightforward driver with solid project potential. This car shows its age cosmetically and will need attention, but it still offers a strong platform for someone who wants an affordable entry point with usable running gear. Engine starts, transmission goes into gear, and the chassis has the kind of old-school mechanical simplicity that makes it appealing to DIY owners. Best suited for a handy buyer looking for a budget commuter, parts donor, or restoration candidate. Priced to move and reflects current condition.",
